nsity and size of networks. Based on analysis of the\nalgorithms and numerical simulations, we propose a hybrid approach providing\ncompetitive accuracy with improved computational efficiency.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 22 Apr 2018 21:11:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 16 Jan 2020 22:00:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-20"}
