ize the derived tight lower bound.\nSimulation results show that compared with existing algorithms, the system\nperformance can be greatly improved by the proposed algorithms in terms of both\nsum MSE and sum SE.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Apr 2018 14:27:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-24"}
